data.description: Beautiful Split level on large fenced corner lot. Covered porch entry opens into tiled foyer with adjoining formal Dining Room and Living Room/Office and leads to central area featuring large Kitchen with Cafe area and Gathering Room. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are separated by Retreat/Game Room and share full bath. Owner's Suite and Bath occupy most of the other side of homes downstairs with large Tun and separate shower and large walk in closet. Stairs lead to Bonus Room/4th Bedroom and Bath and large walk in closet. Perfect for guests or extended family. Garage entry into kitchen , Laundry, 1/2 Bath and staircase to Bonus Room. Large and with screened porch overlooking wood deck with Pergola covered Bar-B-Que area.  Storage shed does convey.
